---
title: Grid Blocks
---

<div class="row">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <h1>Block Grids</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row u-mb-5">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <p>Block grids allow us to evenly split list items within a grid by specifying the number of items per row. Grid blocks inherently add a negative left and right offset so it is flush with the edge of the column it is in.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row u-mb-3">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <h2>Standard Block Grid</h2>
    <p>The following markup will generate an even distribution of 4 blocks per row.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row u-mb-5">
  <div class="example">
    <div class="row show-grid">
      <div class="small-12 columns">
        <ul class="small-block-grid-4">
          <li><span>1</span></li>
          <li><span>2</span></li>
          <li><span>3</span></li>
          <li><span>4</span></li>
          <li><span>5</span></li>
          <li><span>6</span></li>
          <li><span>7</span></li>
          <li><span>8</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <pre>
    <code><%= display_code('
<div class="row">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <ul class="small-block-grid-4">
      <li>1</li>
      <li>2</li>
      <li>3</li>
      <li>4</li>
      <li>5</li>
      <li>6</li>
      <li>7</li>
      <li>8</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>') %></code>
  </pre>
</div>

<div class="row u-mb-3">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <p>Generating a 3 column block grid is just as simple.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row u-mb-5">
  <div class="example">
    <div class="row show-grid">
      <div class="small-12 columns">
        <ul class="small-block-grid-3">
          <li><span>1</span></li>
          <li><span>2</span></li>
          <li><span>3</span></li>
          <li><span>4</span></li>
          <li><span>5</span></li>
          <li><span>6</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <pre>
    <code><%= display_code('
<div class="row">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <ul class="small-block-grid-3">
      <li>1</li>
      <li>2</li>
      <li>3</li>
      <li>4</li>
      <li>5</li>
