  </pre>
</div>

<div class="row u-mb-3">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <h2>Block Grids Without Gutters</h2>
    <p>If we need an evenly distributed grid of blocks without gutters, we add the class <code>.block-grid-collapse</code> to our <code>ul</code>.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row u-mb-5">
  <div class="example">
    <div class="row show-grid">
      <div class="small-12 columns">
        <ul class="small-block-grid-4 block-grid-collapse">
          <li><span>1</span></li>
          <li><span>2</span></li>
          <li><span>3</span></li>
          <li><span>4</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <pre>
    <code><%= display_code('
<div class="row">
  <div class="small-12 columns">
    <ul class="small-block-grid-4 block-grid-collapse">
      <li>1</li>
      <li>2</li>
      <li>3</li>
      <li>4</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>') %></code>
  </pre>
</div>